Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.65,0:00:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if entrance exams only start \Nonce you're in your third year.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have a real advantage if you start preparing early.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that, but I imagine students \Nhave lots of things to worry about.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a study session!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get together with anything you don't understand,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.16,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mafuyu can tutor you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not struggling.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.13,0:01:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! You're not...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.01,0:01:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a little?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I'm particularly \Nhaving trouble with in my studies.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a student like that exists!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.72,0:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they do. That's how these girls are.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.81,0:01:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You expect me to believe that there are actually magical girls who do well in school?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all magical girls bad at studying?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're late!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.86,0:01:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,According to our data,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.94,0:01:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tee hee!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the only conclusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.82,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that so.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some prejudice.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.84,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,A study session?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.22,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,That'd really help!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.22,0:02:04.31,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,I need help with a lot of my subjects...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.77,0:02:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that's what they'd say.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I report to Mafuyu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.57,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're younger than me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could help them out in some way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.74,0:02:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to do something all \Nstudents do, try a study session.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A study session...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect magical girls to actually do {\i1}well{\i0} in school.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help out.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're partners, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miton!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.60,0:02:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he could have \Njust asked us out for tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. You're right!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I asked you, Chiya!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just assume that we're friends now?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just keep quiet when Yuzuka's around.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.20,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yuzuka's not here,\Nyou will address me by my surname.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll engrave it into my brain, Sakagami-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going out for tea?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mafuyu-san has invited us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,On Saturday, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her know, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.72,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,That was easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This Saturday, would you like to admire \Nand appreciate Yuzuka with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what should I say?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what would make me sound more grown up...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's responded.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.61,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,I'd like to admire and appreciate \Nyou too, Chiya-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd I do? How'd I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.63,Default - Italics,,0,0,0,,That is a conversation best saved for another time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued.
